OL,3,CBishop of Durham retires after a
OL,4,Cdecade of championing the disadvantaged
OL,6,FHelen Ford went to meet the Bishop of
OL,7,FDurham as he retires.
OL,9,FThe Bishop of Durham says he has
OL,10,F"mixed emotions" as he retires from
OL,11,Fhis duties after ten years.
OL,13,FThe Right Reverend Paul Butler, who
OL,14,Fhas served as the Bishop of Durham for
OL,15,Fa decade, stood down from his position
OL,16,Fon 29 February 2024.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, Bishop Paul
OL,19,Fsaid: "I know it's the right time to
OL,20,Fbe stepping down. They've been ten
OL,21,Famazing years.
