OL,3,CBishop of Durham retires after a
OL,4,Cdecade of championing the disadvantaged
OL,6,F"Ten very full, very busy years and
OL,7,FI've loved being here and I've loved
OL,8,Fbeing the Bishop of Durham but also
OL,9,Fknow it's the right time to go."
OL,11,FBishop Paul is the most senior figure
OL,12,Fin the Church of England in the North
OL,13,FEast.
OL,15,FOver the past decade he has championed
OL,16,Fsome of the issues facing people
OL,17,Fthroughout the North East, including
OL,18,Fsupporting low income households and
OL,19,Frefugees.
