OL,6,FHe said: "It arises absolutely out of
OL,7,Fmy Christian faith and my following of
OL,8,FJesus but also from the fact that this
OL,9,Fregion has such high degrees of
OL,10,Fpoverty, particularly child poverty
OL,11,Fand children and young people have
OL,12,Fbeen a concern of mine the whole of my
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,F"The region, also, has had a lot of
OL,16,Fasylum seekers and refugees through
OL,17,Fdispersal systems and so on.
