OL,6,F"One of the things that surprised me
OL,7,Fwhen I became Bishop of Durham is just
OL,8,Fhow important the role is seen by
OL,9,Flocal authority leaders and local
OL,10,Fpeople so I was encouraged by leaders
OL,11,Facross the region so I was sort of
OL,12,Farmed and charged with doing so."
OL,14,FLast May the Bishop received worldwide
OL,15,Fattention when he played a leading
OL,16,Frole in the Coronation of King Charles
OL,17,FIII.
OL,19,FDuring the service,That meant
OL,20,Fescorting the King everywhere during
OL,21,Fthe coronation service.
