OL,6,FHistorically, the Bishop of Durham
OL,7,Fhave been involved with the coronation
OL,8,Fof new monarchs over hundreds of years.
OL,10,FOn this honour, Bishop Paul continued:
OL,11,F"It was an enormous privilege, a huge
OL,12,Fhonour to be that close to him,
OL,13,Fsupporting him, guiding him through.
OL,14,F"There was a moment during it when I
OL,15,Fdid find myself thinking - pinch
OL,16,Fyourself - this can't be happening.
OL,17,FAfterwards I was taken aback by how
OL,18,Fmuch local people said to me 'It felt
OL,19,Flike we were there'."
