OL,6,FOn his departure from the region, the
OL,7,FRight Reverend Paul Butler shared it
OL,8,Fwas his pleasure to serve the people
OL,9,Fof the North East.
OL,11,FHe continued: "I shall take loads and
OL,12,Floads of memories of wonderful people
OL,13,Fbecause actually, for all the
OL,14,Fstruggles, the region is full of
OL,15,Famazing wonderful people.
