OL,6,F"I'm not thinking of famous people at
OL,7,Fall here. It's just the ordinary
OL,8,Fpeople that it's my privilege to meet
OL,9,Fin parishes, in communities who are
OL,10,Fcaring for the elderly, supporting the
OL,11,Fyoung, helping to make their
OL,12,Fcommunities work so it's all that I
OL,13,Fwill take away alongside the beauty of
OL,14,Fthe dales and the sea."
